LANDLORDS

A FRIENDLY & DEPENDABLE SERVICE FOR LANDLORDS & TENANTS

Established back in 1986, Park Lane Properties has over twenty years’ experience of residential property management and currently handles over 100 properties in the Newmarket and Cambridge area, from small city flats to country houses.

Our aim is to deal with both landlords and tenants with the minimum of fuss and the maximum of efficiency. As landlords ourselves we treat our clients’ properties as we do our own and fully understand the importance of controlling costs, organising maintenance, respecting our tenants - and, of course, collecting the rent on time!
